         <div type="translation">
            <ab>". . . 1 ounce of rue (?), . . . kotylae of rose oil, 3 ounces or pounds of lettuce, . . . of wax, 4 lbs. of iron rust, . . . fenugreek, 6 lbs. of willow root, 6 oz. of kolophonian resin. Add the fenugreek and the expressed juice of willow root to the oil and boil over a fire until four "fingers" are left remaining. Then sprinkle the dried ingredients over the liquid, mix together and strain through a linen cloth. Raise it . . ."</ab>
